WEBVTT

00:24.960 --> 00:25.880
Your Highness,

00:26.480 --> 00:27.960
know how to swim?

00:29.320 --> 00:30.240
Swim?

00:33.880 --> 00:34.680
Swim?

00:36.280 --> 00:37.640
So that is how it is.

00:37.720 --> 00:40.720
Xie Zheng planned
to break the dam from the start.

00:40.800 --> 00:42.200
So he only brought a thousand men.

00:47.480 --> 00:49.360
Well played, Marquis Wu'an.

00:49.440 --> 00:51.760
A small stake for enormous gain.

01:00.320 --> 01:01.160
It is a trap.

01:01.760 --> 01:02.920
Do not advance!

01:03.000 --> 01:06.400
All units fall back!

01:12.440 --> 01:16.200
All units fall back!

01:48.080 --> 01:50.160
The mantis stalks the cicada,
unaware of the oriole behind.

01:50.760 --> 01:52.800
They never imagined
you had another move prepared.

01:52.880 --> 01:54.400
This will trap Xie Zheng for good.

01:54.480 --> 01:58.680
From this day forward, you will
be the sole heir of Prince Changxin.

02:03.360 --> 02:04.200
This is bad.

02:05.400 --> 02:07.600
The manor lies lower. It will flood first.

02:09.520 --> 02:11.320
Master, where are you going?

02:11.400 --> 02:12.600
Do not act rashly.

02:14.640 --> 02:16.120
Wrong way, Master!

02:16.200 --> 02:17.400
That way leads to the manor.

02:32.680 --> 02:34.960
-Are you hurt?
-I am fine.

02:46.600 --> 02:47.560
What is this thing?

02:49.040 --> 02:50.160
Cang.

02:51.200 --> 02:53.200
What do you think it does?

02:53.760 --> 02:55.000
There is a cord here.

02:55.520 --> 02:56.440
Pull it and see.

02:59.480 --> 03:03.000
HE

03:06.360 --> 03:08.640
Your scouts are loyal to the end.

03:09.160 --> 03:11.120
Still trying to warn you.

03:12.200 --> 03:14.480
Why not try escaping, Sui Yuanqing?

03:23.400 --> 03:25.080
SUI

03:28.360 --> 03:30.360
Xie Qi. Take him away.

03:34.400 --> 03:35.360
Who told you to pull that?

03:35.440 --> 03:36.400
He told me to!

03:38.040 --> 03:38.880
He pulled it.

03:39.760 --> 03:40.600
He says jump, you jump?

03:41.920 --> 03:42.760
Want a beating?

03:44.480 --> 03:45.560
-Yuanbao!
-What were you thinking?

03:45.640 --> 03:46.640
Yuanbao!

03:46.720 --> 03:47.880
Hit him!

03:47.960 --> 03:48.960
Harder!

03:49.040 --> 03:50.160
I understand now.

03:50.240 --> 03:51.760
That man pretended to beg for mercy.

03:51.840 --> 03:54.400
He was buying time to signal.
The thing Master Tao wanted me to stop…

03:56.360 --> 03:57.200
was this.

03:59.320 --> 04:02.120
Marquis, the wound is serious.
It must be treated at once.

04:03.000 --> 04:05.000
I know my condition. Keep this quiet.

04:06.640 --> 04:08.840
That temper of yours
truly needs softening.

04:10.080 --> 04:11.240
Let me see.

04:12.240 --> 04:13.440
She's still burning with fever.

04:16.079 --> 04:19.000
Ning has been on the run for days
and badly frightened.

04:19.079 --> 04:21.120
This illness will take time to heal.

04:21.880 --> 04:23.120
Where shall we settle her?

04:24.240 --> 04:25.680
Once she improves,

04:25.760 --> 04:26.960
send her back to Jizhou.

04:27.680 --> 04:29.120
Changyu's probably

04:29.200 --> 04:30.760
pacing the floor at home.

04:32.120 --> 04:32.960
Ning,

04:33.480 --> 04:34.760
this is candy from Changyu.

04:35.320 --> 04:36.320
Do you miss her?

04:38.840 --> 04:39.680
Have some.

04:42.600 --> 04:43.880
Have you learned your lesson?

04:43.960 --> 04:45.080
Who goes there?

04:45.920 --> 04:47.400
How dare you signal the rebels?

04:48.080 --> 04:48.960
Who are you?

04:50.600 --> 04:52.720
We are scouts under Marquis Wu'an.

04:52.800 --> 04:56.680
That in your hands
is a Sui army warning flare.

05:00.960 --> 05:03.120
We are laborers repairing the dam.

05:03.200 --> 05:06.320
An enemy discovered the breach plan
and tried to warn the rebel army.

05:07.040 --> 05:08.240
We finished him off.

05:09.600 --> 05:11.680
If not for us dealing with those scouts,

05:12.320 --> 05:14.240
the Marquis's plan would have failed.

05:16.440 --> 05:17.760
Here are the scouts' tokens.

05:17.840 --> 05:19.440
Check them if you doubt us.

05:22.920 --> 05:24.480
Then this is a misunderstanding.

05:25.160 --> 05:27.160
You have courage.

05:28.760 --> 05:30.440
What are your names?

05:31.040 --> 05:32.000
‎We are…

05:32.600 --> 05:34.640
Stay modest. No need to claim merit.

05:39.000 --> 05:39.840
Marquis.

05:42.040 --> 05:43.360
General He sends urgent word.

05:43.440 --> 05:45.880
Rebel General Shi Yue has surrounded us.

05:47.120 --> 05:48.400
Marquis, Strategist,

05:49.000 --> 05:50.280
you must break through at once.

05:51.240 --> 05:54.160
Shi Yue is Prince Changxin's
fiercest commander.

05:54.240 --> 05:55.680
Seasoned and relentless.

05:56.280 --> 05:57.400
How many troops?

05:58.080 --> 05:59.200
Thirty thousand.

05:59.280 --> 06:00.160
Thirty…

06:03.760 --> 06:05.480
We have suffered heavy losses.

06:05.560 --> 06:07.080
Fewer than 800 left.

06:07.160 --> 06:08.960
Even breaking through
would be near impossible.

06:10.080 --> 06:12.680
The mantis stalks the cicada,
never seeing the oriole behind.

06:15.200 --> 06:17.760
Xie Wu. Ensure Changning
is settled safely.

06:17.840 --> 06:18.680
Yes.

06:19.920 --> 06:22.840
Marquis, you intend to stay?

06:24.440 --> 06:26.240
You have fewer than a thousand men.

06:26.320 --> 06:28.040
How will you face tens of thousands?

06:28.720 --> 06:30.120
My Yanzhou main force

06:30.200 --> 06:31.600
is already marching toward Baxia.

06:32.640 --> 06:35.040
Return and inform General He

06:36.080 --> 06:37.760
I will meet him at Beigu Mountain

06:38.360 --> 06:39.760
around the Spring Equinox.

06:39.840 --> 06:40.720
Understood.

06:41.320 --> 06:42.440
General,

06:42.520 --> 06:43.720
withdraw your troops.

06:44.400 --> 06:46.360
Shi Yue wants the Xie army.

06:46.440 --> 06:49.160
As long as Sui Yuanqing
and our forces remain here,

06:49.680 --> 06:51.760
he will not waste men chasing you.

06:51.840 --> 06:52.760
But…

06:55.040 --> 06:57.960
Marquis, Strategist, take care.

06:59.360 --> 07:00.480
Take care.

07:01.600 --> 07:03.560
Jizhou forces, withdraw!

07:04.320 --> 07:09.240
MARQUIS WU'AN

07:09.320 --> 07:10.960
By my command,

07:11.040 --> 07:12.280
strike camp.

07:12.840 --> 07:15.000
Move to Beigu Camp.

07:26.840 --> 07:30.480
Marquis Wu'an's army truly is formidable.

07:30.560 --> 07:32.720
They look impressive.

07:42.240 --> 07:45.840
May Heaven protect the Marquis.

07:47.000 --> 07:50.280
May our soldiers march in strength
and return in peace.

08:04.760 --> 08:06.680
Report! The dam at Baxia has burst.

08:06.760 --> 08:08.440
Sui forces suffered heavy losses.

08:08.520 --> 08:10.960
His Highness has been… captured
by the Marquis Wu'an.

08:11.720 --> 08:14.400
Shi Yue, Xie Zheng has gone too far.

08:14.480 --> 08:15.360
He'll pay with his life!

08:15.440 --> 08:16.440
Shi Hu.

08:16.520 --> 08:17.480
SHI YUE

08:17.560 --> 08:19.520
At times like this, we remain calm.

08:21.880 --> 08:23.600
-Fortunately, Master foresaw this
-Yes.

08:23.680 --> 08:24.760
and had us positioned here.

08:25.440 --> 08:27.280
Now we have the Marquis surrounded.

08:28.400 --> 08:31.080
We will meet this Marquis Wu'an.

08:32.240 --> 08:35.120
Then find a way to rescue His Highness.

08:49.640 --> 08:51.160
Master Tao!

08:51.760 --> 08:53.800
Tao, we are back!

08:57.360 --> 08:58.800
Master Tao!

09:07.200 --> 09:10.400
It is done. The Marquis has won.

09:11.960 --> 09:12.920
‎We won.

09:13.000 --> 09:14.360
We have won!

09:14.960 --> 09:15.880
We have won!

09:15.960 --> 09:16.880
We have won!

09:17.800 --> 09:18.880
It is done.

09:18.960 --> 09:19.840
‎We won the battle!

09:22.800 --> 09:24.000
Excellent.

09:27.080 --> 09:29.400
Who says women are lesser than men?

09:30.880 --> 09:31.960
Taking you as my disciple

09:33.960 --> 09:36.400
was a choice well made.

11:05.000 --> 11:08.600
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

12:24.760 --> 12:25.960
Yu Qianqian.

12:26.720 --> 12:29.280
Wake up. Yu Qianqian.

12:29.360 --> 12:31.000
I will not let you die.

12:47.760 --> 12:48.760
Qian.

13:24.440 --> 13:25.800
Where are we going?

13:27.440 --> 13:28.520
Does it matter?

13:30.200 --> 13:31.680
Where I go, you go.

13:32.760 --> 13:34.440
You do not leave my side.
Not for a moment.

14:01.440 --> 14:03.840
Stop! Stop! I cannot hold it anymore!

14:08.280 --> 14:10.720
-Young Master, slow down.
-Uncle Xun, my stomach hurts.

14:10.800 --> 14:12.200
Watch your step.

14:20.480 --> 14:21.880
Careful now.

14:21.960 --> 14:23.080
Nanny Lan,

14:23.160 --> 14:24.440
we are nearing Jizhou territory.

14:24.520 --> 14:27.400
Will Marquis Wu'an
truly join forces with us?

14:27.480 --> 14:30.160
Shi Yue's 30,000 troops stand before him.

14:30.240 --> 14:31.640
He may not even save himself.

14:33.320 --> 14:35.560
Shi Yue is fierce and cunning,

14:35.640 --> 14:37.440
but his opponent is Marquis Wu'an.

14:37.520 --> 14:40.320
Nothing is decided yet. Master…

14:42.480 --> 14:45.160
Qi Min and Sui Yuanqing
laid trap upon trap,

14:45.240 --> 14:47.880
and the Marquis broke them
all with fewer men.

14:48.400 --> 14:49.680
I trust

14:49.760 --> 14:51.640
this time, he will prevail as well.

14:52.840 --> 14:53.640
Who is there?

15:37.640 --> 15:39.640
Nanny, did you truly believe

15:39.720 --> 15:41.680
you could spirit that child away,

15:41.760 --> 15:43.520
escape safely,

15:45.000 --> 15:47.160
and throw yourself
under the Marquis's protection?

15:49.000 --> 15:51.480
It seems you have forgotten

15:52.200 --> 15:53.520
what Mother once entrusted to you.

15:55.320 --> 15:56.920
It is precisely because I remember

15:57.000 --> 15:59.480
that I must choose rightly.

16:00.160 --> 16:02.760
The Crown Princess died pitifully,

16:02.840 --> 16:06.280
giving her life to preserve someone
as unhinged as you.

16:07.040 --> 16:08.920
Have you forgotten the hatred
of Crown Prince Chengde?

16:09.000 --> 16:10.760
Have you forgotten

16:10.840 --> 16:12.920
how your mother burned to death
before your eyes?

16:17.720 --> 16:18.640
I feel much better.

16:20.360 --> 16:21.200
Bao'er.

16:23.320 --> 16:24.840
I remember.

16:25.480 --> 16:29.960
I remember Father being cut open
by the Northern Jue.

16:30.480 --> 16:32.120
I remember

16:32.680 --> 16:35.360
my own flesh blistering in the flames.

16:36.560 --> 16:38.360
The pain burned so deep

16:38.440 --> 16:40.600
that even now,
I barely feel anything at all.

16:41.760 --> 16:42.920
And I remember

16:44.240 --> 16:47.120
Mother's screams as she burned alive.

16:54.280 --> 16:55.280
Live.

17:02.120 --> 17:03.160
And you

17:04.560 --> 17:06.079
cloak betrayal

17:06.800 --> 17:09.119
in righteous words.

17:20.960 --> 17:25.079
As long as the green hills remain!

17:25.160 --> 17:27.560
As long as the green hills remain!

17:28.840 --> 17:31.480
As long as the green hills remain!

17:50.800 --> 17:51.760
So.

17:53.360 --> 17:55.320
You have finally decided

17:56.400 --> 17:58.480
to kill the child

17:59.560 --> 18:01.000
you raised.

18:02.880 --> 18:04.400
But I do not intend to die just yet.

18:10.840 --> 18:11.840
What will you do?

18:22.600 --> 18:25.560
An emperor must never
be blinded by sentiment.

18:25.640 --> 18:27.880
You may deceive the entire realm,

18:27.960 --> 18:30.800
yet a single woman
has you spinning in circles.

18:31.400 --> 18:33.600
You love Yu Qianqian so deeply.

18:35.640 --> 18:36.880
Did you know

18:37.760 --> 18:39.920
she has said more than once

18:40.000 --> 18:43.680
that only your death
would keep Bao'er alive?

18:58.600 --> 19:02.120
I meant to take her with us.

19:02.200 --> 19:03.560
She said

19:03.640 --> 19:06.640
as long as you lived,
we could never escape.

19:07.800 --> 19:09.240
She said

19:10.000 --> 19:14.520
she would kill you with her own hands.

19:34.200 --> 19:35.240
I tried to kill you.

19:36.880 --> 19:38.360
Why would you still save me?

19:39.400 --> 19:41.160
Your life belongs to me.

19:41.240 --> 19:42.640
Without my permission,

19:43.440 --> 19:45.920
no one gets to take it.

19:51.640 --> 19:53.880
Young Master, we must go.

20:09.640 --> 20:11.040
When you see Mother,

20:12.040 --> 20:13.280
give her my respects.

20:27.560 --> 20:29.640
-Bury her properly.
-Yes.

20:29.720 --> 20:30.880
Zhao Xun and the young…

20:31.960 --> 20:33.720
"As long as the green hills remain."

20:34.760 --> 20:36.760
That was not meant for me.

20:37.280 --> 20:38.840
They are close.

20:39.520 --> 20:40.840
I want them alive.

20:40.920 --> 20:42.640
Yes. Search!

21:05.000 --> 21:06.760
You were willing to throw away your life

21:06.840 --> 21:08.440
to kill me

21:08.520 --> 21:10.640
for that boy's safety.

21:11.840 --> 21:13.480
But you hesitated at the end. Why?

21:15.720 --> 21:17.120
Who says I hesitated?

21:17.720 --> 21:20.480
If I fail once, I will try again.

21:21.160 --> 21:22.080
If I fail twice,

21:22.760 --> 21:23.800
there will be a third time.

21:23.880 --> 21:25.840
One day, I will kill you.

21:28.680 --> 21:30.000
If you kill me,

21:30.680 --> 21:32.840
someone else will kill that boy.

21:33.680 --> 21:36.240
If not once, then twice.

21:36.880 --> 21:38.200
If not twice,

21:39.840 --> 21:41.440
then a third time.

21:43.040 --> 21:46.080
If you harm Bao'er,
I won't live without him.

21:47.880 --> 21:49.160
That is exactly why…

21:52.080 --> 21:55.240
our little family of three
must all remain alive.

22:00.720 --> 22:07.640
BEIGU MOUNTAIN MILITARY CAMP

22:13.480 --> 22:14.960
You are wounded. Stop walking around.

22:15.040 --> 22:16.600
-Go back and lie down.
-I am fine.

22:17.680 --> 22:20.560
If I do not show myself,
who will steady the troops?

22:21.120 --> 22:21.960
Careful.

22:23.600 --> 22:25.840
Beigu Camp may be old,

22:25.920 --> 22:28.440
but the ground favors defense.
Easy to hold, hard to take.

22:29.040 --> 22:31.480
And there were already
several hundred stationed here.

22:31.560 --> 22:33.920
-Shi Yue will not storm it easily.
-Let go of me!

22:34.880 --> 22:36.560
With such a tattered camp,

22:37.680 --> 22:38.880
you think to hold the line?

22:40.560 --> 22:41.880
You are finished.

22:42.800 --> 22:44.320
Marquis, how shall we handle him?

22:45.120 --> 22:46.080
Lock him in the dungeon.

22:46.160 --> 22:47.840
Yes. Take him away.

22:48.480 --> 22:49.840
You are all dead!

22:51.120 --> 22:52.720
Dead!

22:55.720 --> 22:56.560
Marquis.

22:57.080 --> 22:58.920
Yesterday, a few dam laborers

22:59.000 --> 23:01.440
encountered enemy scouts
and killed three of them.

23:01.520 --> 23:03.560
By sheer luck,
they stopped the warning flare.

23:03.640 --> 23:04.960
That is how Sui Yuanqing
walked into the trap.

23:05.720 --> 23:07.720
Were their names recorded?

23:07.800 --> 23:10.400
They have rendered service.
Jizhou must reward them.

23:11.240 --> 23:12.760
Recorded, Strategist.

23:13.280 --> 23:16.040
Northwest Pig-Slaughter Squad.
Hard to forget a name like that.

23:16.720 --> 23:18.080
What are your names?

23:19.360 --> 23:21.320
Stay modest. No need to claim merit.

23:22.040 --> 23:23.240
We should introduce ourselves.

23:26.480 --> 23:27.680
We are…

23:28.720 --> 23:32.600
-Northwest Pig-Slaughter Squad.
-Northwest Pig-Slaughter Squad.

23:39.120 --> 23:40.960
Northwest Pig-Slaughter Squad…

23:41.040 --> 23:42.080
You may leave.

23:42.160 --> 23:43.000
Yes.

23:46.600 --> 23:48.520
Northwest Pig-Slaughter Squad.

23:49.320 --> 23:51.040
That name is certainly memorable.

23:53.520 --> 23:55.080
It reminds me of someone.

23:59.000 --> 24:00.040
Impossible.

24:00.800 --> 24:03.240
She is in Jizhou with Li Huai'an,
searching for Ning.

24:05.240 --> 24:06.320
Still, you are right.

24:07.040 --> 24:08.200
Since Ning is safe,

24:09.200 --> 24:10.920
we should send word.

24:11.000 --> 24:12.040
No need to let her worry.

24:24.120 --> 24:25.440
It is only temporary.

24:28.000 --> 24:28.920
Ms. Fan.

24:29.000 --> 24:31.120
Most of the barracks were destroyed.

24:31.200 --> 24:32.600
Please rest here for now.

24:34.160 --> 24:35.000
Thank you.

24:35.640 --> 24:36.840
And my men?

24:37.920 --> 24:39.440
Grand Tutor Tao took them to settle in.

24:40.080 --> 24:41.760
The kitchen's buns today

24:41.840 --> 24:43.400
are hard as the iron we hammer.

24:43.480 --> 24:44.920
I took a bite earlier.

24:45.000 --> 24:46.520
Nearly broke my teeth.

24:47.120 --> 24:49.000
Mr. Zhao, is this spear fit for use?

24:50.160 --> 24:53.240
The spearhead must be tempered
at the right heat.

24:53.320 --> 24:56.200
Too brittle and it will snap.

24:56.800 --> 24:57.800
Pay attention next time.

24:58.960 --> 25:00.200
Mr.… Mr. Zhao.

25:00.280 --> 25:02.040
BLACKSMITH

25:07.280 --> 25:08.440
Changyu?

25:13.640 --> 25:14.880
Mr. Zhao…

25:16.120 --> 25:16.960
Changyu!

25:18.200 --> 25:19.240
Mr. Zhao!

25:20.360 --> 25:21.840
Changyu, what are you doing at the camp?

25:23.760 --> 25:24.600
I…

25:26.360 --> 25:27.680
Mrs. Chen,

25:28.360 --> 25:29.680
Mrs. Zhuang,

25:30.600 --> 25:31.920
Mrs. Tao,

25:32.800 --> 25:34.200
and Kang Hu.

25:36.800 --> 25:38.240
They are alive.

25:42.920 --> 25:45.320
Poor Constable Wang and Kang.

25:46.040 --> 25:47.520
Gone just like that.

25:53.600 --> 25:54.840
And Ning is still missing.

25:59.000 --> 26:00.240
Listen, Changning

26:00.920 --> 26:03.760
has a round face, blessed features.
She will be all right.

26:06.640 --> 26:09.520
I will find her.
No matter how long it takes.

26:11.280 --> 26:13.360
You take care of yourself too.

26:13.440 --> 26:15.080
Mrs. Zhao is waiting at home for you.

26:16.640 --> 26:18.000
I am managing.

26:18.080 --> 26:21.840
I can treat livestock.
When I was young, I learned some smithing.

26:22.440 --> 26:23.560
Here in camp,

26:23.640 --> 26:26.600
shoeing horses, tending animals,

26:26.680 --> 26:28.520
mending blades,

26:28.600 --> 26:31.120
they all rely on me.

26:32.040 --> 26:34.320
As for Jin Yuanbao and those rascals,

26:34.400 --> 26:36.080
they surprised me.

26:36.160 --> 26:37.640
Imagine that.

26:37.720 --> 26:39.720
Stopped their petty mischief

26:39.800 --> 26:41.880
and joined the army. Not a bad turn.

26:48.000 --> 26:49.800
You've been in camp all this time.

26:50.360 --> 26:52.040
Have you heard from Yan Zheng?

26:52.920 --> 26:54.400
Did the bundle reach him?

26:57.480 --> 27:00.160
I had someone send it along.

27:00.240 --> 27:01.600
But I did not see him myself.

27:03.040 --> 27:04.280
I asked around.

27:04.360 --> 27:06.560
He is not with this supply column.

27:09.440 --> 27:12.240
There is an old saying in the army.

27:13.400 --> 27:15.680
If there is no death notice,
then it is good news.

27:16.520 --> 27:19.320
Do not worry. Yan Zheng will be fine.

27:19.960 --> 27:21.960
And when he rises in rank one day,

27:22.040 --> 27:24.480
you will share in his fortune.

27:26.280 --> 27:28.920
Actually, we are divorced.

27:35.400 --> 27:36.680
What happened?

27:37.720 --> 27:39.720
It was never a true marriage.

27:39.800 --> 27:42.680
A temporary arrangement to deal
with Uncle and protect the house.

27:43.360 --> 27:46.040
Once that was settled, he had to leave.

27:46.120 --> 27:47.240
But…

27:47.320 --> 27:48.840
Changyu.

27:48.920 --> 27:50.880
From what I saw,

27:50.960 --> 27:53.480
Yan Zheng was never indifferent to you.

27:56.080 --> 27:58.000
You're both young.

27:58.080 --> 28:01.200
At your age, passions run high.
People make rash choices.

28:01.920 --> 28:03.440
If you meet again someday,

28:03.520 --> 28:06.680
you must talk this through
with him properly.

28:06.760 --> 28:09.680
Do not let it become an old regret
that lingers for a lifetime.

28:16.480 --> 28:20.240
If he is alive,
I will clear this up with him.

28:21.280 --> 28:23.240
And I truly can read faces.

28:23.320 --> 28:27.000
Yan Zheng has a long, fortunate look.
He will be just fine.

28:31.280 --> 28:32.120
Grand Tutor Tao.

28:34.240 --> 28:35.640
Changyu.

28:36.360 --> 28:37.720
Changyu.

28:46.160 --> 28:49.480
First thing,
you get the furnace blazing hot. Fast.

28:49.560 --> 28:51.360
Then work the bellows.

28:51.960 --> 28:52.840
And when you pull,

28:52.920 --> 28:55.280
match it to the hammer's rhythm.

28:55.360 --> 28:57.320
Once the iron turns red, we strike.

28:57.400 --> 29:00.520
Forging is all about the rhythm.
Keep it steady. Look.

29:02.080 --> 29:05.000
This girl…
Won't sit still to study with me,

29:05.080 --> 29:07.200
but happily runs off to learn smithing.

29:08.520 --> 29:09.960
All right. That will do.

29:10.040 --> 29:11.680
Mr. Zhao.

29:11.760 --> 29:13.240
We are here for the new weapons.

29:13.320 --> 29:14.720
All ready. Right here.

29:15.640 --> 29:17.680
Careful. Heavy.

29:17.760 --> 29:19.160
I will help.

29:19.240 --> 29:21.160
Careful, Changyu. They are weighty.

29:21.800 --> 29:23.480
-Bring another bundle.
-Another one?

29:23.560 --> 29:24.800
-You sure you can?
-Of course.

29:24.880 --> 29:25.720
All right.

29:27.240 --> 29:28.080
-One more.
-All right.

29:28.160 --> 29:29.200
Here, one more.

29:31.120 --> 29:33.600
Changyu, that strength of yours

29:33.680 --> 29:35.240
is no weaker than Fan Erniu's.

29:36.120 --> 29:37.360
Not even close to my father.

29:37.440 --> 29:39.440
He could lift me and my mother
with one hand.

29:40.120 --> 29:41.200
Incredible!

29:41.800 --> 29:42.720
-Impressive.
-Yeah.

29:42.800 --> 29:44.040
Truly impressive.

29:47.440 --> 29:48.800
Watch out!

29:50.280 --> 29:53.640
-Mr. Zhao, are you hurt?
-Changyu, what are you doing?

29:57.560 --> 29:58.640
Mr. Zhao.

30:01.000 --> 30:02.600
Quick, quick. Take this.

30:04.720 --> 30:05.960
Are you all right, Mr. Zhao?

30:06.560 --> 30:07.720
Nothing to worry about.

30:07.800 --> 30:09.680
I only got my foot clipped.

30:09.760 --> 30:11.760
-Come here.
-I am fine. Fine.

30:13.000 --> 30:15.040
Why are you helping him first?

30:15.120 --> 30:17.520
Why not me? Who is he?

30:17.600 --> 30:19.160
-Master Tao, come.
-Careful.

30:21.240 --> 30:22.080
Slowly.

30:23.160 --> 30:24.640
Careful now.

30:24.720 --> 30:25.560
Careful.

30:26.880 --> 30:27.720
Here.

30:30.120 --> 30:31.720
Why does he get the chair

30:31.800 --> 30:33.480
and I get the wooden stump?

30:35.520 --> 30:36.400
Fine, you sit here.

30:37.080 --> 30:38.200
Let's go sit over there.

30:46.680 --> 30:47.520
What is it?

30:49.160 --> 30:51.280
Perhaps I've stood by that furnace longer

30:51.360 --> 30:52.640
than I should have.

30:52.720 --> 30:54.800
The heat went straight to my chest.

30:54.880 --> 30:56.200
My whole body aches.

30:56.280 --> 30:58.280
I will brew you some medicine.

31:04.560 --> 31:05.400
And you? What is wrong?

31:05.480 --> 31:07.480
My head hurts.

31:07.560 --> 31:08.920
Your head?

31:09.440 --> 31:11.960
That spear shaft
did not even touch your head.

31:13.520 --> 31:15.800
Must be that night's chill catching up.

31:15.880 --> 31:17.080
Come. Let's see the army doctor.

31:17.160 --> 31:18.160
I am not going anywhere.

31:18.240 --> 31:19.800
I will recover right here.

31:21.400 --> 31:22.640
Fine.

31:22.720 --> 31:24.720
You two stay here and rest.

31:24.800 --> 31:26.000
I'll brew the medicine.

31:27.600 --> 31:29.960
Changyu, mine must simmer first.

31:30.040 --> 31:31.600
Otherwise, I refuse to drink it.

31:34.360 --> 31:35.800
Why are you acting like a child?

31:35.880 --> 31:36.960
Arguing over who goes first?

31:38.400 --> 31:41.800
Relax. I will brew two pots at once.
No first, no second.

31:41.880 --> 31:43.840
Then I will drink first.

31:43.920 --> 31:44.840
All right.

32:05.560 --> 32:07.240
Changyu told me.

32:07.320 --> 32:09.320
You exchanged fate with her

32:09.400 --> 32:10.960
to save her life.

32:14.800 --> 32:16.560
That was righteous.

32:19.240 --> 32:20.480
For that alone,

32:20.560 --> 32:22.840
I should yield you
the first bowl of medicine.

32:23.400 --> 32:25.480
You are too generous.

32:25.560 --> 32:27.800
I almost want to kowtow to you
on her behalf.

32:27.880 --> 32:30.520
Please, no need. Get up, please.

32:34.920 --> 32:37.880
You have known Fan Changyu long?

32:37.960 --> 32:39.080
Of course.

32:39.720 --> 32:42.480
We have been neighbors
for nearly 20 years.

32:42.560 --> 32:43.880
She is like a daughter to me.

32:44.720 --> 32:46.400
I will be honest.

32:46.480 --> 32:49.080
I have never seen a finer girl.

32:49.160 --> 32:50.760
Indeed.

32:50.840 --> 32:53.480
Nor have I seen a better young woman.

32:57.680 --> 32:58.960
Have some warm water.

32:59.040 --> 33:00.080
It settles the stomach.

33:00.760 --> 33:02.080
Good.

33:02.720 --> 33:05.080
Let's take tea as wine.

33:06.880 --> 33:07.920
Please.

33:08.000 --> 33:09.040
-Please.
-Please.

33:27.720 --> 33:29.560
Where did this unit come from?

33:29.640 --> 33:30.800
Oh.

33:30.880 --> 33:32.640
That is the Jizhou supply convoy.

33:32.720 --> 33:35.240
They are here to restock the camps
near Wu River.

33:39.440 --> 33:41.720
We are missing one herb. Prunella.

33:43.480 --> 33:45.200
You might find it in the kitchen.

33:46.000 --> 33:47.000
Thank you.

33:52.760 --> 33:53.840
Greetings, Lord Li.

33:54.480 --> 33:56.800
-Who is inside?
-A few wounded soldiers.

33:56.880 --> 33:59.160
-And Mr. Zhao.
-Mr. Zhao?

34:03.040 --> 34:04.600
How badly are you hurt, Mr.--

34:08.080 --> 34:11.159
Li Wenkan. What did you just call me?

34:12.760 --> 34:15.360
I am three years older
than your grandfather.

34:17.840 --> 34:19.679
Grand Tutor Tao. What are you doing here?

34:23.080 --> 34:24.360
Listen to me rambling.

34:24.440 --> 34:26.920
I forgot to tell Changyu
you arrived today.

34:27.000 --> 34:28.280
Changyu?

34:28.880 --> 34:30.199
Who arrived?

34:36.120 --> 34:37.600
-Why are you here?
-Why are you here?

34:38.760 --> 34:40.159
So the heroine everyone in camp praises

34:40.239 --> 34:42.120
for chasing down enemy scouts is you.

34:42.760 --> 34:43.920
You are not hurt?

34:44.000 --> 34:45.639
No. Thank you for your concern, Lord Li.

34:47.080 --> 34:48.719
Still calling me Lord after all this time?

34:48.800 --> 34:50.280
That sounds awfully distant.

34:51.320 --> 34:53.159
My courtesy name is Wenkan.
You may call me that.

34:57.240 --> 34:58.360
It means

34:58.440 --> 35:00.800
that however long I've studied,
I remain but a student.

35:05.320 --> 35:06.640
You hold high office.

35:06.720 --> 35:08.680
How could I presume
to address you so freely?

35:08.760 --> 35:11.240
But I will remember it.
Li Wenkan. It does sound nice.

35:15.640 --> 35:16.680
I'll take that as praise.

35:17.960 --> 35:20.160
That Li fellow's no good cookie.

35:20.880 --> 35:22.320
What cookie? Is it tasty?

35:23.520 --> 35:25.560
I'm saying he doesn't sit right with me.

35:26.560 --> 35:28.120
You are heading to Lucheng?

35:29.280 --> 35:31.600
The supplies must reach Lucheng
within seven days.

35:32.200 --> 35:34.640
I do not know what General He
and the Marquis are planning,

35:34.720 --> 35:36.000
but as the convoy commander,

35:36.080 --> 35:38.120
I will see the supplies delivered on time.

35:39.640 --> 35:41.520
Shall I send someone
to see you back to Jizhou?

35:42.120 --> 35:43.720
There may already be news of Ning.

35:43.800 --> 35:46.040
I left two men behind
to continue searching for her.

35:48.400 --> 35:49.920
Then I truly owe you my thanks.

35:51.000 --> 35:52.040
Come on. Stop gawking.

36:02.680 --> 36:04.240
That… That is our falcon.

36:06.360 --> 36:07.880
Yan Zheng…

36:18.600 --> 36:20.320
Long time no see, silly bird.

36:20.400 --> 36:21.360
Still as plump as ever.

36:26.960 --> 36:27.800
Off you go.

36:35.000 --> 36:40.720
CHANGNING AND I ARE SAFE. I'LL HAVE HER
ESCORTED HOME. REST EASY. YAN ZHENG

36:41.320 --> 36:42.240
"Changning…

36:42.920 --> 36:43.840
Safe…

36:44.400 --> 36:45.320
Yan Zheng."

36:47.680 --> 36:50.280
Does it say Yan Zheng found Changning?

36:52.040 --> 36:53.080
It says Changning is safe.

36:54.040 --> 36:55.360
Yan Zheng is safe as well.

36:56.160 --> 36:58.760
He says not to fret.
He'll send her home soon.

37:03.360 --> 37:04.200
Good.

37:07.120 --> 37:08.800
That's good.

37:10.640 --> 37:11.840
Changning is safe.

37:13.080 --> 37:14.320
Yan Zheng is safe.

37:16.680 --> 37:18.920
Good. That's good.

37:23.600 --> 37:24.640
My lord.

37:26.200 --> 37:27.080
It is urgent.

37:28.320 --> 37:30.000
‎-We got spots inside.
‎-Thank you.

37:30.080 --> 37:31.280
‎HE

37:31.360 --> 37:33.480
That is all the news we have for now.

37:33.560 --> 37:34.920
What do you two make of it?

37:39.600 --> 37:40.440
Master Tao.

37:41.120 --> 37:42.120
Here, Mr. Zhao.

37:44.920 --> 37:46.160
Careful!

37:48.280 --> 37:49.240
It is hot.

37:54.200 --> 37:55.600
Why are you not drinking?

37:58.720 --> 38:00.000
Lord Li,

38:00.080 --> 38:02.400
what did you mean earlier?

38:02.480 --> 38:03.600
I did not quite follow.

38:03.680 --> 38:05.160
In plain terms,

38:05.240 --> 38:08.280
Marquis Wu'an is besieged,
with provisions running thin.

38:10.760 --> 38:12.800
He intends to hold Beigu Mountain

38:12.880 --> 38:14.840
and keep Shi Yue's army tied down.

38:14.920 --> 38:17.680
It is a ploy.

38:17.760 --> 38:22.160
He must prevent Shi Yue
from joining forces with Prince Changxin.

38:23.080 --> 38:25.080
If Beigu Mountain falls

38:25.160 --> 38:28.360
and those armies unite,
Lucheng will be lost.

38:28.440 --> 38:30.200
Once that happens, Jizhou cannot stand.

38:32.600 --> 38:33.960
What matters most now

38:34.040 --> 38:37.040
is getting supplies up that mountain.

38:37.120 --> 38:38.600
Then I will go.

38:38.680 --> 38:40.000
Shi Yue, even if he is made of iron,
I don't care.

38:40.080 --> 38:41.600
I will get the grain there.

38:41.680 --> 38:42.720
Ms. Fan, absolutely not.

38:42.800 --> 38:43.920
It is too dangerous.

38:44.000 --> 38:44.840
He is right.

38:44.920 --> 38:47.280
This is not work for common townsfolk.

38:47.360 --> 38:49.880
We do what we can here at Wu River Camp.

38:49.960 --> 38:51.520
That is enough.

38:51.600 --> 38:53.200
What are you going for? To die?

38:54.320 --> 38:55.320
If I don't go,

38:55.400 --> 38:56.680
Lord Li must take the grain to Lucheng,

38:56.760 --> 38:58.200
and he cannot be spared. So who goes?

38:59.800 --> 39:01.800
Marquis Wu'an fights for people like us.

39:01.880 --> 39:03.440
I cannot let him starve.

39:05.360 --> 39:06.880
Mr. Zhao.

39:06.960 --> 39:08.600
Please let me go.

39:08.680 --> 39:10.320
And if something happens to you?

39:10.400 --> 39:11.960
How am I to answer to my wife?

39:12.040 --> 39:13.080
To Ning?

39:13.160 --> 39:15.440
To your parents in the next world?

39:16.040 --> 39:17.040
Do not worry.

39:17.120 --> 39:19.560
I have my own team now.
I can look after myself.

39:19.640 --> 39:22.080
And how exactly do you plan to do that?

39:23.600 --> 39:24.800
Such spirit.

39:24.880 --> 39:27.200
Just as I saw in you from the start.

39:28.600 --> 39:30.720
Why are you encouraging her?

39:32.000 --> 39:34.560
She's no common butcher woman anymore.

39:34.640 --> 39:36.760
She can lead men into battle.

39:48.480 --> 39:49.760
Move fast. No hesitation.

39:50.400 --> 39:51.720
Obey orders to the letter.

39:51.800 --> 39:52.840
Yes!

39:53.400 --> 39:54.560
Advance!

40:07.120 --> 40:09.360
SUI

40:10.640 --> 40:13.960
Marquis, torches below stretch for miles.

40:14.040 --> 40:16.440
At a glance, no fewer than 30,000.

40:32.200 --> 40:33.040
Xie Zheng.

40:34.360 --> 40:35.760
Tell me straight.

40:35.840 --> 40:37.240
What is your thinking?

40:37.320 --> 40:38.760
Keep men watching their movements.

40:39.960 --> 40:40.800
Yes.

40:42.840 --> 40:45.640
The Marquis chose his ground well.

40:45.720 --> 40:48.360
Only one narrow hidden path leads up.

40:48.440 --> 40:50.920
If we rush in, they can strike first.

40:52.240 --> 40:54.840
Easy to defend. Hard to breach.

40:55.760 --> 40:58.480
When he stormed Northern Jue
and slaughtered Jinzhou,

40:59.040 --> 41:01.560
it was no stroke of luck.

41:01.640 --> 41:04.760
Shi Yue, if we cannot find
another way up tonight,

41:04.840 --> 41:06.360
we must force an assault at dawn.

41:06.440 --> 41:07.560
No.

41:08.520 --> 41:10.840
His Highness is still in their hands.

41:10.920 --> 41:12.280
We cannot move recklessly.

41:14.400 --> 41:16.480
With Sui Yuanqing as our hostage,

41:16.560 --> 41:18.200
we stall as long as we can.

41:18.280 --> 41:20.000
Now we shall see

41:20.080 --> 41:21.200
whether He Jingyuan fails me.

41:23.480 --> 41:24.680
Xie Wu.

41:24.760 --> 41:26.760
How long will our grain last?

41:26.840 --> 41:29.160
If the men eat properly, ten days.

41:29.240 --> 41:31.080
If we thin it with wild greens,
half a month.

41:35.320 --> 41:37.480
The mountain paths are treacherous.

41:37.560 --> 41:39.640
Shi Yue surrounds but does not attack.

41:39.720 --> 41:41.960
He means to trap us here
and starve us out.

41:43.120 --> 41:44.880
A turtle in a jar.

41:46.400 --> 41:49.160
Who is the jar and who is the turtle
remains to be seen.

41:49.680 --> 41:50.720
Report!

41:51.360 --> 41:54.320
Marquis, a Jizhou supply unit
fought their way up the mountain.

41:55.120 --> 41:56.440
They broke through Shi Hu's blockade?

41:57.360 --> 41:59.120
Yes. Heavy casualties.

42:01.280 --> 42:03.880
-See they are properly treated.
-Yes.

42:05.120 --> 42:06.960
General. A supply unit
climbed the mountain

42:07.040 --> 42:09.200
by a side path. Our vanguard spotted them.

42:09.880 --> 42:11.920
We planned to ambush from behind,

42:12.000 --> 42:13.680
but the Xie army intervened.

42:13.760 --> 42:16.200
In the clash, we killed
a dozen from their supply unit.

42:16.280 --> 42:17.800
Still, several were rescued

42:17.880 --> 42:19.120
by the Xie forces.

42:20.040 --> 42:21.440
How did you guard the mountain?

42:22.280 --> 42:23.720
At such a time, you let grain through?

42:24.440 --> 42:25.560
Useless lot!

42:27.400 --> 42:29.360
It was only a handful.

42:30.200 --> 42:34.200
That little grain would not fill a mouth.
Nothing to fear.

42:36.080 --> 42:37.640
What did they carry?

42:37.720 --> 42:40.400
We found grain on the bodies.

42:40.480 --> 42:43.720
And in the abandoned carts below,
we found salt and herbs.

42:45.000 --> 42:47.520
They must be short on manpower,

42:48.160 --> 42:50.880
forced to abandon everything but grain.

42:55.680 --> 42:57.400
Short on salt?

42:59.240 --> 43:01.320
That is very good news.

43:09.240 --> 43:10.080
Marquis.

43:11.120 --> 43:13.640
Two female military physicians
from the supply unit

43:14.160 --> 43:15.160
request an audience.

43:19.080 --> 43:20.040
Female physicians?

43:23.400 --> 43:24.320
Let them in.

46:03.240 --> 46:06.240
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:06.320 --> 46:07.240
Subtitle Translation by: Jiaxin Wang
